hadiths[22]{hadithnumber,text}:
5351,"maine unse puchha kya tum us hadis ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kartey ho. unhon-ne kaha ke ji haan , Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab musalman apne ghar main apne joru baal bachchon par Allah ka hukm ada karne ki niyat se kharch karey to usmein bhi usko sadqey ka sawab milta hai."
5352,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala farmata hai ke aey ibne-Aadam! to kharch kar to main tujh ko diye jaaunga.
5353,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke bewaon aur miskinon ke kaam aaney wala Allah ke rastey mein jihad karne waley ke barabar hai, ya raat bhar ibadat aur din ko rozey rakhney waley ke barabar hai."
5354,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) meri iyaadat ke liye tashrif laaiye . main us waqt Makka Mukarrama mein bimar tha. maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha ke mere paas maal hai. kya main apne tamam maal ki wasiiyat kar dun? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi. maine kaha phir aadhey ki kar dun? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi ! maine kaha, phir tehai ki kar dun ( farmaya ( tehai ki kar do aur tehai bhi bahut hai. agar tum apne waarison ko maaldaar chhod kar jao ye us se behtar hai ke tum unhein mohtaaj w tang dast chhodo ke logon ke samney wo hath phailaatey phirein aur tum jab bhi kharch karogey to wo tumhari taraf se sadqa hoga. yahan tak ke us luqme par bhi sawab milega jo tum apni biwi ke munh mein rakhney ke liye uthaaogey aur ummeed hai ke abhi Allah tumhen zinda rakhega, tum se bahut se logon ko nafa pahunchega aur bahut se doosrey (kaafir) nuqsan uthaaengey."
5355,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke sabse behtreen sadqa wo hai jisey de kar dene wala maaldaar hi rahe aur har haal mein uper ka hath ( dene waley ka ( nichey ke) leney waley ke) hath se behtar hai aur) kharch ki) shuruaat unse karo jo tumhari nigahbaanii mein hain. aurat ko us mutaalbe ka haq hai ke mujhey khana de warna talaaq de. ghulam ko us mutalba ka haq hai ke mujhey khana do aur mujh se kaam lo. betaa keh sakta hai ke mujhey khana khilaao ya kisi aur par chhod do. logon ne kaha : aey Abu-Hurera ! kya (ye aakhiri tukda bhi) ke joru kehti hai aakhir tak. aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai? unhon-ne kaha ke nahi balke ye Abu-Hurera ki khud apni samajh hai.
5356,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke behtreen khairat wo hai jisey dene par aadmi maaldaar hi rahe aur shuruaat unse karo jo tumhari nigrani mein hain jinke khilaaney pahnaaney ke tum zimme daar ho.
5357,"tum ne aisey shakhs ke barey mein bhi suna hai jo apne ghar walon ke liye saal bhar ka ya saal se kam ka kharch jama kar ley. Mamar ne bayan kya ke us waqt mujhey yad nahi aaya phir baad mein yad aaya ke is barey mein aik hadis ibne-Shahab ne ham se bayan ki thi, unse Malik bin Aus ne aur unse ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bani Nazir ke baagh ki khajoorein bech kar apne ghar walon ke liye saal bhar ki rozii jama kar diya kartey they."
5358,"mujhey Malik bin Aus bin hadsaan ne khabar di (ibne-Shahaab Zohri ne bayan kya ke) Muhammad-bin Juber bin Mut-im ne iska kuchh hissey bayan kya tha, isliye main rawaana hua aur Malik bin Aus ki khidmat mein pahuncha aur unse ye hadis poochhii. Malik ne mujh se bayan kya ke main umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to unke darbaan Yarfaa unke paas aaey aur kaha Usman-bin-Affan , Abdur-Rehman , Zaid aur Sad (Raziallahu anhu) (aap se milney ki) ijazat chahtey hain kya aap unhein uski ijazat dengey ? umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke andar bula lo. chunanche unhein uski ijazat de di gaee. rawi ne kaha ke phir ye sab andar tashrif laey aur salam karke baith gaey. Yarfaa ne thodi der ke baad phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) se aa kar kaha ke Ali aur Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bhi milnaa chahtey hain kya aap ki taraf se ijazat hai? umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bhi andar bulaney ke liye kaha, andar aa kar un hazraat ne bhi salam kya aur baith gaey. iske baad Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, ameerul-momineen mere aur un ( Ali (Raziallahu anhu)) ke darmyan faisla kar dijiye. doosrey sahaba Usman (Raziallahu anhu) aur unke sathiyon ne bhi kaha ke ameerul-momineen unka faisla farma dijiye aur unhein us uljhan se nijat dijiye. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha jaldi na karo main Allah ki qism de kar tum se poochhta hun jiske hukm se aasman w zameen qaaim hain. kya tumhen malum hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya hai hamara koi waaris nahi hota, jo kuchh ham anbiya wafat ke waqt chhodtey hain wo sadqa hota hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ishara khud apni zaat ki taraf tha. sahaba ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye irshad farmaya tha. iske baad umr (Raziallahu anhu) Ali aur Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf mutwajjeh huey aur unse puchha mein Allah ki qism de kar aap se poochhta hun, kya aap logon ko malum hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye irshad farmaya tha. unhon-ne bhi tasdeeq ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne waqei ye farmaya tha. phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ab main aap se us maamle mein baat karunga . Allah Taala ne apne rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko us maal mein Mukhtar kal honey ki khusoosiyat bakhshii thi aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke siwa usmein se kisi doosrey ko kuchh nahi diya tha. Allah Taala ne irshad farmaya thaa ما أفاء الله على رسوله منهم فما أوجفتم عليه من خيل‏ se ( qadeer ( tak. '' isliye ye ( char khums ( khas aap ke liye they. Allah ki qism Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tumhen nazar andaz karke us maal ko apne liye khas nahi kar liya tha aur na tumhara kam karke usey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne liye rakha tha, balke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pahley tum sab mein uski taqseem ki aakhir mein jo maal baqi reh gaya to usmein se aap apne ghar walon ke liye saal bhar ka kharch letey aur uske baad jo baqi bachta usey Allah ke maal ke kharch hi main (musalmanon ke liye) kharch kar detey. aap ne apni zindagi bhar usi ke mutabiq amal kya. aey Usmaan! main tumhen Allah ki qism deta hun, kya tumhen ye malum hai? sab ne kaha ke ji haan, phir aap ne Ali aur Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se poochha, main tumhen Allah ki qism deta hun, kya tumhen ye bhi malum hai? unhon-ne bhi kaha ke ji haan malum hai. phir Allah Taala ne apne Nabi ki wafat ki aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka khaleefa hun. chunanche unhon-ne us jaaidaad ko apne qabze mein ley liya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke amal ke mutabiq usmein amal kya. Ali aur Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf mutwajjeh ho kar unhon-ne kaha, aap donon us waqt maujood they, aap khub jantey hain ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne aisa hi kya tha aur Allah janta hai ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) usmein mukhlis, mohtaat w nek-niiyat aur sahi rastey par they aur haq ki ittaba (pairvi) karne waley they. phir Allah Taala ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki bhi wafat ki aur ab main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ka jaa-nasheen hun. mein 2 saal se us jaaidaad ko apne qabze mein liye huey hon aur wahi karta hun jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne usmein kya tha. ab aap hazraat mere paas aaey hain, aap ki baat aik hi hai aur aap ka mamla bhi aik hai. aap (Abbaas (rz)) aaey aur mujh se apne bhatijey (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) ki wiraasat ka mutalba kya aur aap (Ali (Raziallahu anhu)) aaey aur unhon-ne apni biwi ki taraf se unke walid ke tarke ka mutalba kya. maine aap donon se kaha ke agar aap chaahein to main aapko ye jaaidaad de sakta hun lekin us shart ke sath ke aap par Allah ka ahad wajib hoga. wo ye ke aap donon bhi us jaaidaad mein wahi tarze-amal rakhengey jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne rakha tha, jiske mutabiq Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne amal kya aur jab se main iska wali hua hun, maine jo iske sath mamla rakha aur agar ye shart manzoor na ho to phir aap mujh se is barey mein guftgu chhodein. aap logon ne kaha ke us shart ke mutabiq wo jaaidaad hamarey hawale kar do aur maine usey us shart ke sath tum logon ke hawale kar diya. kyon Usman aur unke saathiyon! mein aapko Allah ki qism deta hun maine us shart hi par wo jaaidaad Ali aur Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke qabze mein di hai naa? unhon-ne kaha ke ji haan. rawi ne bayan kya ke phir aap Ali aur Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf mutwajjeh huey aur kaha, main aap hazraat ko Allah ki qism deta hun kya maine aap donon ke hawale wo us shart ke sath ki thi? donon hazraat ne farmaya ke ji haan. phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya, kya aap hazraat ab iske siwa mujh se koi aur faisla chahtey hain? us zaat ki qism hai jiske hukm se aasman w zameen qaaim hain iske siwa main koi aur faisla qiyamat tak nahi kar sakta. ab log uski zimme-dari poori karne se aajiz hain to mujhey wapas kar dein main iska bando-bast aap hi kar loonga."
5359,"Hind binte- Utba (Raziallahu anhu) hazir huin aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! Abu-Sufiyan (unke shauhar ( bahut kanjoos hain, to kya mere liye usmein koi gunah hai agar main unke maal mein se (iske peeth peechhey ( apne bachchon ko khilaaun ? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi, lekin dastoor ke mutabiq hona chahiye"
5360,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar aurat apne shauhar ki kamaaii mein se, iske hukm ke baghair (dastoor ke mutaabiq) Allah ke raaste mein kharch kar de to usey bhi aadha sawab milta hai."
5361,"Fatima (Raziallahu anha) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein ye shikayat karne ke liye hazir huin ke chakkii peesney ki wjah se unke hathon mein kitni takleef hai. unhein malum hua tha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas kuchh ghulam aaey hain lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se unki mulaqat na ho sakii. isliye Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se iska zikr kya. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey to Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne aap se iska tazkira kya. Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey yahan tashrif laey (raat ke waqt) ham us waqt apne bistaron par let chukey they ham ne uthna chaha Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum donon jis tarah they isi tarah raho. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere aur Fatima ke darmyan baith gaey. maine aap ke qadmon ki thandak apne pet par mehsus ki. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, tum donon ne jo cheez mujh se mangi hai, kya main tumhen us se behtar aik baat na bata dun? jab tum (raat ke waqt) apne bistar par let jao to 33 martaba ( sub'haanallaah ( , Mina 33 martaba (alhamdulillah) aur 34 martaba ( Allahu-akbar ( padh liya karo ye tumharey liye londi ghulam se behtar hai."
5362,"Fatima (Raziallahu anha) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui thin aur aap se aik khaadim maanga tha, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kya main tumhen aik aisi cheez na bata dun jo tumharey liye us se behtar ho. sotey waqt tentis ( 33 ( martaba ( sub'haanallaah ( , Mina tentis ( 33 ( martaba ( alhamdulillah (aur chauntis ( 34 ( martaba ( Allahu-akbar ( padh liya karo. Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne kaha ke unmein se aik kalima chauntis baar keh ley. Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke phir maine un kalimon ko kabhi nahi chhoda . unse puchha gaya jange-siffain ki raaton mein bhi nahi? kaha ke safain ki raaton mein bhi nahi."
5363,"ghar main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kya kya kartey they? Ummul-Momenin (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghar ke kaam kya kartey they, phir aap jab azan ki awaz suntey to bahar chaley jatey they."
5364,Hind binte- Utba ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! Abu-Sufiyan (unke shauhar) kanjoos hain aur mujhey itna nahi detey jo mere aur mere bachchon ke liye kafi ho sakey. haan agar main unki laa-ilmii mein unke maal mein se ley loon (to kaam chalta hai). Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum dastoor ke muwafiq itna ley sakti ho jo tumharey aur tumharey bachchon ke liye kafi ho sakey.
5365,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke oont par Sawar honey wali aurton mein (yani Arab ki aurton mein) behtreen auratein qureshi auratein hain. doosrey rawi ( ibne- Taaus ( ne bayan kya ke Quraish ki Saleh , nek auratein ( sirf lafz qureshi aurton ke bajaey) bachchey par bachpan mein sabse zyada meharban aur apne shauhar ke maal ki sabse zyada hifazat karne waaliyaan hoti hain. Muawiya aur Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aisi hi riwayat ki hai."
5366,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey mera kapdey ka joda hadiye mein diya to maine usey khud pahan liya, phir maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chehra Mubarak par narazgi dekhi to maine usey phaad kar apni aurton mein taqseem kar diya."
5367,"mere walid Shahid ho gaey aur unhon-ne saat (7) ladkiyan chhodiin ya (raawii ne kaha ke) nau (9) ladkiyaan. chunanche maine aik pahley ki shadi shuda aurat se nikah kya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se malum farmaya ke Jaabir! tum ne shadi ki hai? maine kaha ji haan. farmaya, kunwari se ya biyaahii se. maine arz kya ke biyaahii se. farmaya tum ne kisi kunwari ladki se shadi kyon na ki. tum iske sath kheltey aur wo tumharey sath kheltii. tum iske sath hansii-mazaaq kartey aur wo tumharey sath hansi karti. Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke is par maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kya ke Abdullah ( mere walid ( Shahid ho gaey aur unhon-ne kai ladkiyan chhodi hain, isliye maine ye pasand nahi kya ke unke paas un hi jaisi ladki biyaah laaun, isliye maine aik aisi aurat se shadi ki hai jo unki dekh bhaal kar sakey aur unki islaah ka khayal rakhey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke Allah tumhen barkat de ya (raawii ko shak tha) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( kheeraa . Mina ( farmaya yani Allah tum ko khair ata kare."
5368,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aik sahib aaey aur kaha ke main to halaak ho gaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aakhir kya baat huii? unhon-ne kaha ke maine apni biwi se Ramazan mein ham-bistarii kar li. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir aik ghulam aazad kar do. (ye kaffara ho jaaeyga) unhon-ne arz kya ke mere paas kuchh nahi hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir 2 mahiney lagaataar rozey rakh lo. unhon-ne kaha ke mujh mein uski bhi taqat nahi hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir sath miskinon ko khana khilaao. unhon-ne kaha ke itna bhi mere paas nahi hai. iske baad aap ke paas aik tokraa laya gaya jis mein khajoorein thin. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke masla poochhney wala kahan hai? un sahib ne arz kya main yahan hazir hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke lo usey (apni taraf se) sadqa kar dena. unhon-ne kaha apne se zyada zarurat mand par? ya Rasulullah! us zaat ki qism jisne aapko haq ke sath bheja hai, un donon pathreeley maidaanon ke darmyan koi gharaana ham se zyada mohtaaj nahi hai. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hansey aur aap ke Mubarak daant dikhai dene lagey aur farmaya, phir tum hi uske zyada mustahiq ho."
5369,"Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah! kya mujhey abu-Salma (unke pahley shauhar) ke ladkon ke barey mein sawab milega agar main un par kharch karun. main unhein us mohtaajii mein dekh nahi saktii, wo mere betey hi to hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, tumhen har us cheez ka sawab milega jo tum un par kharch karogii."
5370,Hind ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! Abu-Sufiyan kanjoos hain. agar main unke maal se itna ( unse poochhey baghair) ley liya karun jo mere aur mere bachchon ko kafi ho to kya usmein koi gunah hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke dastoor ke mutabiq ley liya karo.
5371,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas jab kisi aisey shakhs ka janaaza laya jata jis par qarz hota to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) malum farmatey ke marney waley ne qarz ki adaaeygi ke liye tarka chhoda hai ya nahi. agar kaha jata ke itna chhoda hai jis se unka qarz ada ho sakta hai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unki Namaz padhtey, warna musalmanon se kehtey ke apne sathi par tum hi Namaz padh lo. phir jab Allah Taala ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par futoohaat ke darwazey khol diye to farmaya ke main musalmanon se unki khud apni zaat se bhi zyada qareeb hun isliye un musalmanon mein jo koi wafat paaey aur qarz chhodey to uski adaaeygi ki zimme-dari meri hai aur jo koi maal chhodey wo uske waarison ka hai."
5372,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! meri behan (aza binte- abi Sufiyaan) binte- abii-Sufiyaan se nikah kar lijiye. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aur tum usey pasand bhi karogii (ke tumhari behan tumhari saukan bin jaaey)? maine arz kya ji haan, us se khali to main ab bhi nahi hun aur main pasand karti hun ke apni behan ko bhi bhalai main apne sath Sharik kar loon. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke ye mere liye jaaiz nahi hai. (2 bahnon ko aik sath nikah mein jama karnaa) maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah! Allah ki qism is tarah ki baatein ho rahi hain ke aap darra binte- abi Salma se nikah ka irada rakhtey hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke Umme-Salma ki betii. jab maine arz kya, ji haan to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar wo meri parwarish mein na hoti jab bhi wo mere liye halal nahi thi wo to mere doodh Sharik bhai ki ladki hai. mujhey aur abu-Salma ko Sobiya ne doodh pilaya tha. isliye tum mere liye apni ladkiyon aur bahnon ko na pesh kya karo aur Shuaib ne bayan kya, unse Zohri ne aur unse Urwa ne, kaha ke Sobiya ko abu-Lahab ne aazad kya tha."
